title: Lunchbox's VIP Treatment + Which Christmas Songs Went #1? + Tenille Townes
itunes:title: Lunchbox's VIP Treatment + Which Christmas Songs Went #1? + Tenille Townes
description:
Luncbox attempts to try and get into a Christmas party as a VIP guest, the crew tries to guess which Christmas songs hit #1 on the billboard charts. Plus, Tenille Townes calls in to answer a rapid fire of Christmas questions from Bobby and more!
